  subnet_ids = [aws_subnet.my_subnet_1.id, aws_subnet.my_subnet_2.id]

  tags = {
    Name = "my_db_subnet_group"
  }
}
```

Make sure to replace `"yourpassword"` with a secure password for your RDS instance. Adjust the region, availability zones, and other configurations as necessary for your specific requirements.

