This Terraform configuration is a basic template and may need adjustments based on specifics, such as the actual domain and port used, the health check endpoint/resource path, and more region-specific configurations as needed for your setup. Also, ensure to define the variables or use Terraform's `data.aws_route53_zone` to fetch the zone ID dynamically if you want to avoid hardcoding your zone ID.

