  vpc_id                  = aws_vpc.vpc2.id
  destination_cidr_block    = aws_vpc.vpc1.cidr_block
  vpc_peering_connection_id = aws_vpc_peering_connection.vpc2_to_vpc1.id
}

output "vpc1_id" {
  value = aws_vpc.vpc1.id
}

output "vpc2_id" {
  value = aws_vpc.vpc2.id
}
```

This code will create two VPCs and set up peering between them in AWS. Make sure to replace placeholder values with actual CIDR blocks and other identifiers necessary to match your setup.

